                <h1>Change Page Color in Google Docs: Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To change the page color in Google Docs, open your document and navigate to the "File" menu. Select "Page setup," and a dialog box will appear. Here, you can find the "Page color" option. Click the color box to choose your desired color and click "OK" to apply. Your page color will instantly change. Enjoy customizing!</p>
